    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are absolutely no dents, scratches, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, smelling fresh and showing zero wear on the premium upholstery or touchpoints. Mechanically, the car performs exactly as it did the day it left the factory, offering a smooth, powerful, and quiet ride with a complete service history included. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly preserved example that will satisfy even the most discerning collector or enthusiast.",
